ballisticarc-tui
==================

This project is a clean-room terminal reimplementation of the
1991 turn-based artillery game "Scorched Earth", originally
designed and developed by Wendell Hicken.

No code, art, sound, or data was copied from the original game
or any subsequent port. The implementation was reconstructed
from publicly available design documentation — the in-game help
pages, the shareware documentation, and third-party feature
write-ups. All re-derived.

